54.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rusty-Williams-Grand-Man-copy-1052x591-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rusty-Williams-Grand-Man-copy-1052x591-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rusty-Williams-Grand-Man-copy-1052x591-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rusty-Williams-Grand-Man-copy-1052x591-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>齐心协力，最终发行了一张由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">Hayley Williams</a>的祖父于 20 世纪 70 年代录制的专辑。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="828" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/paramore-cover-interview-2023-this-is-why-3396051"><b>帕拉莫尔：“我希望没有年轻女性经历我所做的事情”</b></a></li></ul><p>现年 78 岁的 Rusty Williams 大约 50 年前首次创作了这些曲目，但即使是他的孙女也不知道它们的存在，因为当时这些曲目尚未发行。</p><p>当帕拉摩尔主唱最近终于听到这些录音时，她决定帮助他首次将它们商业化发行，乐队的鼓手扎克·法罗同意在他自己的唱片公司 Congrats Records 上发行这张专辑。</p><p>这张专辑名为《Grand Man》，将于 2 月 14 日发售，主打单曲《Knocking (At Your Door)》现已发行。听听下面的曲目，这是一首轻快、温柔的摇滚乐。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Rusty Williams - 敲门（在你的门口）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tZ9cK_xpz2Q?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这可能是老威廉姆斯第一次正式发布自己的音乐，但他确实出现在孙女的 2020 年个人专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/hayley-williams-petals-for-armor-review-2661702">Petals For Armor</a> 》中，当时海莉采样了他的歌曲《Friends Or Lovers》。</p><p> “我没有期待任何事情，而且我已经太老了，无法出名，”拉斯蒂·威廉姆斯说。 “但我只是想知道有人喜欢我所做的事情，并被他们正在听的东西所感动。我希望人们能够看到事情真实发生时的感觉。”</p><h2> <strong>《大男人》曲目列表：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="829" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>《敲你的门》</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="829" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“无法远离”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="829" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“天使之眼”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="829" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&