DFIRE_MUSIC_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA_WILDFIRE_MUSIC_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA_WILDFIRE_MUSIC_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA_WILDFIRE_MUSIC_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在肆虐加州城市部分地区的致命野火发生后，洛杉矶音乐界的 1000 多人正在接受一家慈善机构的支持。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259"><strong>了解更多：</strong>洛杉矶音乐界告诉我们野火的“悲剧性”影响：“这种影响将持续多年”</a></li></ul><p> MusiCares（格莱美奖和唱片学院的非营利机构）表示，自从上周（1 月 8 日星期三）发起“救火行动”以来，已有数十人与我们取得了联系。</p><p>该组织的特蕾莎·沃尔特斯 (Theresa Wolters) 在接受<em>NME</em>采访时表示：“通过我们的接触，令我震惊的是有多少人失去了一切。”</p><p>许多国际知名的音乐家都受到了这场灾难性大火的影响，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-empress-of-and-family-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827984">Empress Of、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-diivs-zachary-cole-smith-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827362">DIIV 的 Zachary Cole Smith</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madlib-launches-fundraiser-to-help-him-and-his-family-rebuild-after-california-wildfires-3828493">Madlib</a> ，他们都在大火中失去了家园。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEs3DB8h2uJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius